description._content: Description: Free fuel on tap. Women taking the thick waste oil piped from an old umbar in the Oil-Fields. Description: At the Tembi Oil-Pumpimg-Station. Washing greens in the water outlet from the plant. Location: Tembi, Persia Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
